00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:02.720
Terima kasih.

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:04.520
Silakan mulai.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:20.560
Kemana dia pergi?

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.080
Mari kita lihat ke sana!

00:03:37.320 --> 00:03:39.920
